                             update_trolls.py

DESCRIPTION
-----------

This script updates the informations of a guild on some tactical website for a
role play game.
Basically, it logs in to the website and calls the updates php webpages.
It suits well to be launched as a cron job.


USAGE
-----

It requires the mechanize python library.
Edit src/update_trolls_settings.py then run update_trolls.py --help for a list
of the availables options.

AVAILABILITY
------------

  get source from github:
  http://github.com/fabriced/update_trolls.py

